\textbf{Funci\'o de distribuci\'o conjunta}: 
\[
\begin{array}{rl}
F_{XY}(x, y)& = P(X \leq x, Y \leq y)=\\ \\
 & = 
\left\{ 
\begin{array}{ccccll}
x < -1 & \text{\'o} & y < -1 & \qquad & & 0 \\ \\
x \geq 1 & \text{i} & y \geq 1 & \qquad & & 1 \\ \\
-1 \leq x < 1 & \text{i} & -1 \leq y < 0 & \qquad & P(X=-1, Y=-1)=&\frac{1}{3}\\ \\
