P(Y < 2 |_{Z=\frac{5}{7}})=\frac{ \int_{-\infty}^2 f_{ZY}(\frac{5}{7}, y) dy } {f_Z(\frac{5}{7})}=
\frac{ \int_{5/7}^2 \; e^{-y} (y-\frac{5}{7}) dy}{e^{-5/7}}=
\frac{ e^{-5/7} - \frac{16}{7} e^{-2} }{e^{-5/7}} = 1-\frac{16}{7} e^{-9/7}
\]



